# ============================================
# AI Platforms Blocked in China/HK/Macau
# ============================================

# Note:
# Gemini and Google AI Studio are intentionally kept in google.list by default.
# They share Google account/session/risk-control infrastructure, and splitting
# them from the main Google line can create cross-country session mismatch.
# Google AI properties are kept under google.list by default.

# > OpenAI / ChatGPT
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ai.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,chatgpt.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openai.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,oaistatic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,oaiusercontent.com
DOMAIN,chat.openai.com.cdn.cloudflare.net
DOMAIN,openaiapi-site.azureedge.net
DOMAIN,openaicom-api-bdcpf8c6d2e9atf6.z01.azurefd.net
DOMAIN,openaicomproductionae4b.blob.core.windows.net
DOMAIN,production-openaicom-storage.azureedge.net

# > Apple Intelligence / ChatGPT Integration
DOMAIN,apple-relay.apple.com
DOMAIN,gspe1-ssl.ls.apple.com

# > Anthropic / Claude
#   Coverage notes:
#   - Claude chat on web / desktop / mobile shared service endpoints
#   - Claude Code in terminal / CLI / IDE integrations / web runner
#   - Cowork in Claude Desktop
#   - Anthropic Console / API / Docs / Support / Status
#   - Claude artifacts / shared outputs / user-hosted asset domains
#   - Claude install entrypoints: claude.ai/install.sh, install.ps1, install.cmd
#
#   Official product references used for scope verification:
#   - docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/setup
#   - claude.com/product/claude-code
#   - claude.com/product/cowork
#   - support.claude.com/.../claude-code-on-the-web
#
#   Note:
#   - Slack / VS Code / JetBrains are delivery surfaces for Claude Code, but their
#     host-app domains are not Anthropic-owned, so they should be routed by their
#     own rulesets instead of being mixed into the Claude block.
#   - Standard CLI install via `npm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code` depends on
#     npm registry / Node.js distribution domains, so Anthropic-owned domains alone
#     do not fully block first-time installation.
#   - Claude Code can also authenticate/run through Bedrock or Vertex AI; those paths
#     would follow AWS / GCP domains rather than Anthropic-owned domains.
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,anthropic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claude.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claude.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claudeusercontent.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,anthropic
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,claude
DOMAIN,widget.intercom.io
DOMAIN,api-iam.intercom.io
DOMAIN,nexus-websocket-a.intercom.io
DOMAIN,browser-intake-us5-datadoghq.com
DOMAIN,o1158394.ingest.us.sentry.io
DOMAIN,registry.npmjs.org

